. **Module documentation sync** - `docs/modules/matching.md` doesn\'t mention `M
atchingProfileIncomplete` state.\n\n4. **Magic numbers** - `code == 1000` in rep
ository is a magic number per `readability.md`.\n\n5. **BDD test completeness** 
